result.execSummary:
The defendant Tina M Flores was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Tina M Flores is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Tina M Flores was found guilty of Resisting an Officer, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.41(1).

30 days county jail, with huber and to commence within 60 days.  Court will allow the defendant to serve the sentence in another county.

2015CM111 (Criminal Damage to property)

45 days county jail, stayed and places the defendant on probation for a period of 1 year. Consecuctive to any other sentence.  Huber and out of county service if revoked.  1 day of sentence credit.
